window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>My name’s Cassia. When my mother died and my father vanished, everything changed.</p> <p>I planned to graduate high school and leave my dark past behind me, until I met two very different guys; bad boy Thames, and football captain Cairo.</p> <p>Except there’s more to these two men than meets the eye. Without warning, I’m caught up in a dangerous love triangle, trapped in a world where angels and demons are fighting for the souls of mankind.</p> <p>I’m being hunted by a monster straight out of the underworld, and I don’t know if I’ll survive long enough to taste forbidden fruit...</p> <p>Torrent is a young-adult paranormal angel romance packed with action and adventure. What if you were in love with heaven AND hell?</p>"; 
